---
title: Speedy Indonesian Style Chicken Noodles with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Sesame Seeds
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Speedy Indonesian Style Chicken Noodles in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R16_W32_UK_QR15758-4_Main_high-b0a40e22.jpg
